r%20wp%3D%22br1%22%20clear%3D%22ALL%22%3E%3Cbr%20wp%3D%22br2%22%20clear%3D%22ALL%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3EFine%20jewelry%2C%20watches%20and%20giftware%20will%20almost%20certainly%20cost%20you%20less%0Aat%20Borsheim's.%20I've%20looked%20at%20the%20figures%20for%20all%20publicly-owned%20jewelry%0Acompanies%20and%20the%20contrast%20with%20Borsheim's%20is%20startling.%20Our%20one-store%20operation%2C%0Awith%20its%20huge%20volume%2C%20enables%20us%20to%20operate%20with%20costs%20that%20are%20fully%2015-20%0Apercentage%20points%20below%20those%20incurred%20by%20our%20competitors.%20We%20pass%20the%20benefits%0Aof%20this%20low-cost%20structure%20along%20to%20our%20customers.%20%3Cbr%20wp%3D%22br1%22%20clear%3D%22ALL%22%3E%3Cbr%20wp%3D%22br2%22%20clear%3D%22ALL%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%20Borsheim's%20sends%20out%20thousands%20of%20selections%20to%20customers%0Awho%20want%20a%20long-distance%20opportunity%20to%20inspect%20what%20it%20offers%20and%20decide%0Awhich%2C%20if%20any%2C%20item%20they'd%20like%20to%20purchase.%20We%20do%20a%20huge%20amount%20of%20business%0Ain%20this%20low-key%20way%2C%20which%20allows%20the%20shopper%20to%20conveniently%20see%20the%20exceptional%0Avalues%20that%20we%20offer.%20Call%20Sean%20Moore%20or%20Karen%20Goracke%20at%0A%3Ca%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.borsheims.com%2F%22%3EBorsheim's%3C%2Fa%3E%20(800-642-4438)%20and%20save%20substantial%20money%20on%20your%20next%20purchase%0Aof%20jewelry.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%3Ctable%20cellpadding%3D%225%22%20width%3D%22100%25%22%20border%3D%220%22%20cellspacing%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%0A%3Ctd%20valign%3D%22TOP%22%20width%3D%2250%25%22%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%3Ctd%20valign%3D%22TOP%22%20width%3D%2250%25%22%3ESincerely%2C%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%0A%3Ctr%3E%0A%3Ctd%20valign%3D%22TOP%22%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%3Ctd%20valign%3D%22TOP%22%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%0A%3Ctr%3E%0A%3Ctd%20valign%3D%22TOP%22%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%3Ctd%20valign%3D%22TOP%22%3EWarren%20E.%20Buffett%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%0A%